  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the prevalence, during the enrolment, of Left
      Ventricular Dysfunction diastolic and/or systolic in patients with diabetes mellitus type 2
      without known or documented heart disease history and recognize its predictive clinical,
      biohumoral and with non-invasive techniques parameters.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
